lenders.name: Jason Baigent
lenders.loan_because:
Healthy Natured @ Healing Nations is a multi-site platform dedicated to promoting holistic therapies, services and products. Each site within the Healing Nations family has a unique and exciting offer whilst remaining true to the overarching mission of "Unite:Transform:Heal".
We believe that through exposure to holistic values, therapies and products alongside community forums, discussion boards and educational initiatives such as holistic therapy training, lifestyle mentoring and spiritual growth through personal change training we can, and will, truly have a positive and transformational impact on our society and world. Education is at the heart of all our sites, but in a style that meets the needs and dreams of the times we live in, rather than imparting of information, it must be a dynamic interaction between people with preformed cultural stereotypes or prejudice removed and utilising the technologies of today and tomorrow. It is our belief that all by uniting people with a shared vision and interest leads to transformation and ultimately heals hearts, removes barriers and frees the spirit to achieve excellence and abundance.
